Louisa and Dark are here too!

Konoha, Aldo, who did everything you told him to,

I thought it was strange to be called for an

to turn out like this.

I shall annihilate these insects!

Mea-sama, leave these guys to me... Dark, let's

Do you really think you can beat me? You were
probably deceived by being told that your sister
would be revived, you fool.

Shut up! Mea-sama will save my sister! You
couldn't do anything... I won't forgive you...

retrieve it.

good.

Ugh... I'm sorry... It's all my fault... Louisa-
sama... Please pass judgment.

Hmmm... For now, let's put you in a cell and think
about what to do next.

This time, it is very significant that we were

thanks to Konoha's protection from Mea's attack.

Although there is some damage to the village, it

It's good that the sacred treasure has been

it's a grave sin.

...I'm sorry... for my lack of power...
